								<div class="title" id="post-title-3780929">
																		The End is Nigh.
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610227429" alt="Jacob Conwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372582)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;" >Jacob Conwell</a></span> <span class="odate time_1524701564 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">26 Apr 2018 00:12</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3780929">
									

<p>Well, here we are. After the collaborative effort of 27 tales, 9 SCP articles, 1 GoI page, and 1 Site Dossier, we have reached the end of the line. Both for this tale series and for what I like to consider the larger Anderson Robotics tale arc. There is probably more ground to cover here. However, eventually, you need to put a signature on something and let it be.</p>
<p>Thank you to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1621343&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1524701564" alt="SunnyClockwork" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1621343)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;">SunnyClockwork</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2221240&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1524701564" alt="Taffeta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2221240)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;">Taffeta</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1524701564" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;">A Random Day</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2038009&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1524701564" alt="TyGently" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2038009)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tygently" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2038009); return false;">TyGently</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1814684); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1814684&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1524701564" alt="GreenWolf" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1814684)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1814684); return false;">GreenWolf</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2887044); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2887044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1524701564" alt="DrBleep" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2887044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2887044); return false;">DrBleep</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aquablack" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3509218); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3509218&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1524701564" alt="AquaBlack" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3509218)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aquablack" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3509218); return false;">AquaBlack</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3129691); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3129691&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1524701564" alt="Modern_Erasmus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3129691)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3129691); return false;">Modern_Erasmus</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3938622); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3938622&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1524701564" alt="The Great Hippo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3938622)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3938622); return false;">The Great Hippo</a></span> for all the feedback.</p>
<p>If you missed the earlier installments of the series they can be found here:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/the-vanishing-of-vincent-anderson">The Vanishing of Vincent Anderson</a></li>
<li><a href="/non-volatile-memory">Non-Volatile Memory</a></li>
<li><a href="/the-best-laid-plans">The Best Laid Plans</a></li>
<li><a href="/volatile-memory">Volatile Memory</a></li>
</ul>
<p>Those of you interested in the rest of the tale arc, check out the Gamma-13 tab <strong><a href="/anderson-robotics-hub">here</a></strong>.</p>
<p>For those of you who have been here since day one, thanks for reading. I do hope you find this a satisfying conclusion for all of our cast of characters.</p>
<p>Thanks for reading.</p>
<p><em>JC</em></p>

