<p>As someone who feel in love with the concept of Anderson Robotics, and SCP, just a few weeks ago, reading through Anderson's story has bittersweet.</p>
<p>Sweet as it is an interesting tale that is enrapturing.</p>
<p>Bitter as I really wanted to right about AR myself. Because robotics and magic are awesome, am I right?</p>
<p>Also what do you mean by the &quot;Now is the dawning of the Age of Butterflies.&quot;</p>

